fulldesc: The Lenovo Thinkcenter All in one AIO Desktop Fullset comes equiped with a HD 19" screen giving you the ultimate experience with excellent performance and versatility. Its Powered by M93p tiny CPU with core intel i5 4th gen processor 8 GB RAM and 256 GB SSD.
Box Contains web conferencing ready : Lenovo 19" Monitor, CPU,FHD Webcam, KB+Mouse,Wifi Dongle, VGA Cables,Power Cables,Speakers
Comes with a variety of ports for all possible needs, USB 3.0,VGA, LAN Port, Display Port,Security Lock,Audio in/out Port.
It comes preinstalled with Windows 10 Pro and MS Office
